    Weizhen Xie, Wilma A. Bainbridge, Sara K. Inati, Chris I. Baker, Kareem A. Zaghloul.  Memorability of words in arbitrary verbal associations modulates memory retrieval in the anterior temporal lobe.  Nature Human Behaviour, 2020; DOI:  10.1038/s41562-020-0901-2
